CRM Analytics dashboards are populated with your data based on queries that you define. Save and organize your queries in interactive CRM Analytics dashboards, and each time you open the dashboard, get the latest results based on available data.

As a sales executive, your day might include viewing a sales leader dashboard. Each component is based on a query, such as a timeline chart showing cumulative opportunity amount for each week of the quarter, or a leaderboard ranking reps by sales (closed won opportunities).

Built-in dashboard interactivity allows you to ask follow-up questions without adding more queries. For example, select an individual's donut chart to filter results and focus on their performance.

If a dashboard can't answer a question, hover over a component and click Explore to create a new query based on the same dataset.
